posting_body: ['Eight Eighty Eight', '888 108th Ave NE , Bellevue, WA, 98004', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 55', 'OR Text', '55', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'Welcome Home to Eight Eighty Eight', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1046 Sq.', 'Ft.', '888 Apartments offers luxury residences on 18 floors with stunning territorial views of downtown Bellevue, Cascade and Olympic mountains.', 'Enjoy detailed designer finishes like custom closets and undermount cabinet lighting in every home.', 'Hotel-inspired amenities include a 19th floor rooftop deck, yoga studio, business center and dog run, to name a few.', 'With an angled design and boutique floor plans, your new home has been maximized for spacious, city living at its finest.', 'Pet Policy', 'No weight restrictions.', 'Breed restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact leasing office for full list of potentially restricted breeds.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Fzdls9npY0']
